Everybody hates paying for stuff they don't need or will never use. Onra Host has the solution to that: Onra Host's NEW Build Your Own VPS!

After months of development, we're happy to announce that the full version of our server builder has been moved to production and is accepting orders!
&lt;center&gt; [**CLICK HERE TO START BUILDING YOUR VPS**](https://www.onrahost.com/vps)

**Break free from cookie-cutter packages.&lt;br /&gt;Get a server built by you, just for you.**&lt;/center&gt;

**How does the pricing work?**&lt;br /&gt;
All servers have a base fee of $2 per month. The base fee includes your first IPv4 address. Simply add on the resources you need.&lt;br /&gt;
**CPUs**: $1 per core&lt;br /&gt;
**RAM**: $0.25 per 128MB&lt;br /&gt;
**HDD Storage**: $0.04 per GB _minimum of 10GB_ &lt;br /&gt;
**SSD Storage**: $0.20 per GB _minimum of 10GB_ &lt;br /&gt;
**Bandwidth**: $0.50 per 250GB

KVM and Xen are both available at the same price!
&lt;hr /&gt;
**Sample Configurations:**

* 1 Core
* 128MB RAM
* 10GB HDD Storage
* 250GB Transfer per month

$4.15/month

* 1 Core
* 256MB RAM
* 15GB SSD Storage
* 250GB Transfer per month

$7.00/month

* 1 Core
* 1GB RAM
* 37GB HDD Storage
* 250GB Transfer per month

$6.98/month
&lt;hr /&gt;
**LIMITED TIME DISCOUNT:** &lt;br /&gt;
For a _limited time only_ we're waiving the base fee on ALL NEW ORDERS! Simply enter coupon code **LETNOBASEFEE** at checkout for $2 off for LIFE! **_This offer is valid until April 30th, 2016!_**
&lt;hr /&gt;
**Top Quality Tech Support:** &lt;br /&gt;
Onra Host is working to raise the bar on tech support quality. We have a team of technical support representatives located in America and England, providing some of the fastest response times in the industry.

The below dynamically-generated image is updated hourly, and shows the average initial response time for support tickets at Onra Host. No canned responses, no broken English, no bad attitudes. Only premium-quality technical support at Low End prices.
